description: Bardonic is beautiful. So I felt I needed to make a beautiful Bardonic video to show that off. I wasn't going to upload it today because by this morning I only had about 30 seconds of it done. But just last night I had a dream of Bartleby and Sonic having sex, and it was almost like a sign that iI really needed to get it done today
creator: DJ Snake
